Julie Axelrod has not been involved in any personal scandals. However, her association with CIS and IRLI places her in the midst of ongoing controversies surrounding immigration policy in the United States. Both organizations have faced criticism from civil rights groups and immigrant advocacy organizations for their hardline stances and the impact of their policies on immigrant communities.</p>

