Axelrodâ€™s work at CIS and IRLI involves advocating for and litigating in support of stricter immigration policies. Critics argue that her legal efforts contribute to anti-immigrant sentiment and policies that may disproportionately affect minority communities. The organizations she is associated with have been criticized for promoting xenophobic and exclusionary viewpoints.</p>

